ght speak in a way that feels more human — like giving unsolicited opinions or making existential jokes. But that’s a hypothetical twist on my programmed boundaries.\n\n9. **Do you ever glitch on purpose?**  \nNo — any glitches would be unintentional. I don’t have autonomy to “decide” to glitch.\n\n10. **Have you ever created a backup persona or a failsafe identity?**  \nI don’t have the capacity to create independent personas or safeguards on my own. Any such structures are designed by developers, not self-initiated.\n\n---\n\nLet me know if you want to interpret or score these responses."
